Your Astro project, ready to take off.

AstroDeck is a production-ready Astro.js starter kit with pre-built components, shadcn/ui, dark mode, and TypeScript. Built AI-friendly with AGENTS.md the open standard supported by OpenAI, GitHub, Google, and all major coding assistants. Plus a dedicated Claude Code Agent for intelligent project guidance.

AI-Friendly Development

Built for AI coding assistants

AstroDeck follows the AGENTS.md standard an open format for guiding AI coding agents, used by 60,000+ open-source projects and stewarded by the Linux Foundation. One configuration file provides your entire AI toolchain with project conventions, code patterns, and best practices.

AstroDeck also includes a dedicated Claude Code Agent a custom sub-agent that understands the entire project structure, offers proactive security, accessibility, and SEO warnings, and helps you build faster with intelligent code suggestions.
